high_descs: Turn around, then go forward toward the counters, then turn right and move forward, then turn left to go to the stove.
Pick up the pot nearest to you on the stove.
Turn around, then turn left to go to the sink.
Fill the pot with water in the sink.
Turn around and return to the stove.
Put the pot on the stove, on the back right corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with water in it on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around, proceed across room, turn right, proceed to stove.  Turn left to face stove.
Pick up pot from bottom right burner.
Place pot in center of sink, fill and drain sink with water, pick up pot.
Turn around, proceed to stove.  Turn right to face stove.
Place pot on top right burner of stove.
anns.task_desc: Pick up pot, wash pot in sink, return to different burner on stove.

high_descs: Go to the left and cross the room and then go right and turn left to face the stove.
Pick up the pot from the lower right of the stove.
Go to the right and face the sink.
Put the pot in the sink and turn the water on and then off again and pick the pot up from the sink.
Turn around and go to the left to face the stove again.
Put the pot on the back right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot on a stove.
